"uid":35656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"794b6cc3432b1cdbcaab0bdac50751e9074578c5","tid":1040099,"uid":10717,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1ca3f576ebd537c42df1e62d571130fd0bdc77d2","tid":1040099,"uid":34643,"like":29,"dislike":12,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"3bb5394b33673af0b8dbb2f91a3e47f13357cdab","tid":1040099,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T00:32:02.000Z","msg":"華為日前公佈旗下首款摺疊屏幕手機 Mate X，這不但是市場首批上市的新款摺機，亦是首批公佈支援 5G 網絡的手機，不過高達 2,299 歐元（折合 HK$20,496）的定價令人卻步。雖然很多手機愛好者不介意出重金去體驗這款 5G 摺機，但還是希望能夠耐用一點。<br />\n<br />\n高層靠估兩年後打柴？華為承認 Mate X 未有測試數據<br />\n<br />\n究竟這個被大陸傳媒稱為「鷹翼」式摺疊設計有幾耐用呢？華為消費業務手機產品線總裁何剛接受大陸傳媒訪問時直言，「具體次數現在還不能說，因為沒有正式上市，華為還要做更多實驗，但是不管怎麼說，我們一定要達到消費者使用以後，至少我覺得不用太長，至少兩年時間不要出現任何問題，滿足消費者日常使用體驗，這是華為的要求。」<br />\n<br />\n高層靠估兩年後打柴？華為承認 Mate X 未有測試數據<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，即是華為本身沒有屏幕和鉸位等可摺疊次數的數據，而且雖然正式發表了，但實驗測試似乎尚未完成。另外，華為高層並非以客觀而科學化，例如一般消費者每天使用手機的次數作為基準去回覆，反而是他個人覺得「不用太長，至少兩年不出現問題」。<span style=\"color: red;\">華為曾表示 Mate X 花了工程師 3 年時間開發，網友相信會不掌握可摺疊次數的數據嗎？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pfxaS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pfxaS2.png&h=a6cb4715&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5ncaS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5ncaS2.png&h=6122cec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73m8tEX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73m8tEX.png&h=95bb9f35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09wTEMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09wTEMC.png&h=6bf034d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fx14MrD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFx14MrD.png&h=7e5646c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n供應商公版方案話3年研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:00:54.000Z","msg":"唔係話幫華為，聽你咁講就知你未做過研發"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"新係研發左3年既你唔會test埋先推出咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw強國唔test就出都係國情黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦，求其做兩隻機械臂去記錄摺機次數，24x7咁試已經好快知結果"},{"pid":"30ec0a1d96483176e1c69d19ba067fdeac71fecf","tid":1040099,"uid":75193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"oppo部升降機都有做啦 <br />\n華為食屎啦"},{"pid":"d05631ca04e04a2b9cac4aecc2ee68cb19bea5b8","tid":1040099,"uid":196625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:32:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔抄埋D DATA 呢"},{"pid":"3db70d459c68ef4d6c605c562d9c01ed2f5a35ee","tid":1040099,"uid":10717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f466cbd524f2749d830813c17da302c02abff9b","tid":1040099,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"805af329552846d6f76c9209e7bc87db4ab1bffa","tid":1040099,"uid":48083,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"8eb403b0446fdea8dd727c2eef2adab321669968","tid":1040099,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"同你講, 呢種機畀samsung一樣都係test唔到, 基本上第一代係要搵消費者姐黎test"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於壽命，三星表示， Galaxy Fold 的螢幕可以摺 20 萬次，若每天開合 100 次，則有 5 年的使用壽命，以換機週期來看， 5 年是很夠用的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2019/02/21/galaxy-fold-launch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2019%2F02%2F21%2Fgalaxy-fold-launch%2F&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td5SOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=816a27bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://bu